cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.CR 

The paper discusses the definition and understanding of semantics in the context of information and language, which is relevant to several sub-categories in computer science. Specifically, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as it deals with natural language processing and understanding. The paper also touches upon artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information theory (cs.IT), and cryptography (cs.CR) in its discussion of information and semantics.
